
   Library::Thesaurus
 =====================

  This is a module to process a slighty augmented ISO Thesaurus. It
contains a certain number of commands to add more functionality and
information over the Thesaurus.

  Is supports ISO2788 thesaurus and Multilingual Thesaurus.

   Requirement
 ===============

  Library::MLang 0.04 -- module for multi-lingue interface


   Authors
 ===========

